songs.title: Al vacio (live)
songs.lyrics:
Todo parece estar
Queriendo cerrar una herida
Lejos de abandonar
Cerca de una despedida
No quiero mas, verte pasar
Solo me quiero sentar a esperar
Lo fueron a matar
Y lo dejaron con vida
Sin sospechar, que todavía respira
No quiero mas
Verte pasar
Solo me quiero sentar a esperar
Que saltes al vacío y que no vuelvas nunca
Y que toda tu vida te mate la culpa de haberme
Robado una parte del alma
Y es lo que a vos te hace falta
Alejarte de acá
Vos quieres enseñar, pero le faltan ideas
Vos sabes señalar, pero espera que te vean
No quiero mas, verte pasar
Solo me quiero sentar a esperar y rogar
Que saltes al vacío y que no vuelvas nunca
Y que toda tu vida te mate la culpa de haberme robado una parte del alma
Y es lo que a vos le hace falta
Que saltes al vacío y que no vuelvas nunca
Y que toda tu vida te mate la culpa de haberme robado una parte del alma
Y es lo que a vos le hace falta
Alejarte de acá
English translation:
Everything seems to be trying to close a wound
Far from abandoning near a farewell
I do not want more, watch you go, I just want to sit and wait
They were to kill him and left him alive
Without suspecting that still breathes
I do not want more, watch you go, I just want to sit and wait
That you jump into the void and never come back
And that in your whole life kills you the guilt
Of having stolen a part of my soul
And it's what you lack to get away from here
You want to teach but you lack ideas
You know point, but expect to see
I do not want more, watch you go, I just want to sit and wait and pray (screaming)
That you jump into the void and never come back
And that in your whole life kills you the guilt
Of having stolen a part of my soul
And to you is what lack
That you jump into the void
And never come back and that in your whole life
Kills you the guilt of having stolen a part of my soul
And it's what you lack to get away from here
Away from here
(please correct it!)
